title: Highest and Lowest Daily High and Low Temperatures, United States, 2000
name: Highest and Lowest Daily High and Low Temperatures, United States, 2000
description: This dataset illustrates the highest daily high temperatures and the lowest daily low temperatures in cities with 50,000 people or more.  A value of -1 means that the data was not applicable.  Also included are the population, name of the city and state, the temperature, the original city ranking, and the inverse ranking to be used only for mapping purposes.
